{{Top|leg}}
The '''Bothan Debris, Incorporated''' was a [[Bothan/Legends|Bothan]] salvage operation that was established on [[Caamas/Legends|Caamas]] by [[Kursk Te'tell]], charged with recovering any equipment or materials that might have survived the destruction of the planet. However, the corporation also worked to cover up the truth behind Caamas's destruction. It was based in a huge crater on the planet, located about seventy miles south of [[Refuge City]].

